query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM patients WHERE name LIKE '%Silva%' OR name LIKE '%Costa%' OR name LIKE '%Lima%') as mock_patients,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM appointments WHERE DATE(startTime) >= '2026-01-14' AND DATE(startTime) <= '2026-01-16') as mock_appointments,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM documents WHERE title LIKE '%Dezembro 2025%' OR title LIKE '%2026%') as mock_documents;
